{"tid":1499153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英文文宣唔夠 大把藍絲鬼","createTime":"2019-08-23T15:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T22:12:42.000Z","uid":63029,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"283fd65a02cc426b408d4e5bda24927db49db2eb","tid":1499153,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"借朋友account<br />\n<br />\n好多本地鬼都係藍絲<br />\n<br />\n出入鬼佬場合，又話riot又話violence<br />\n<br />\n點解？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為佢哋靠SCMP同pearl去理解本地新聞</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n藍絲鬼嘅比例仲多過華人<br />\n<br />\n因為local 藍絲切膚之痛已變中立或淺黃<br />\n<br />\n藍絲鬼住半山、有外國護照、鍾意香港但唔對路可即撇，賣你港之嘛<br />\n<br />\n我夠膽講：藍絲鬼冇出現移向偏黃，甚至更多淺藍變深藍<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n1. 加強英文文宣渠道，散去佢哋會睇到嘅地方，例如體育會、會所、學校<br />\n<br />\n2. 都係綑綁攬炒，切膚之痛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nMerlin Swire係英國桂民海<br />\nMerlin Swire係英國桂民海<br />\nMerlin Swire係英國桂民海</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你以為白皮膚就走得甩？"},{"pid":"e8f60681448875dc37d51b9b1d7f9c5fdc8c835f","tid":1499153,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"9af231b6a217a4cd318ee3b591a0780aa1284ea8","tid":1499153,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"被控義士們依家點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1499004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1499004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"66aba23b1c18db18972b9bcdeccf0a6bb51b703b","tid":1499153,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"f7fd3596301ccd8efe47475050d2902ebfcba488","tid":1499153,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:32:54.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"943e1ebbbd6168d4231dca538dc58987aecc099b","tid":1499153,"uid":15484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019